txt.en: In the distance the sound of laughter is heard
You have discovered the source of the strange laughter
'You have come for the Elf's armour, have you not?'
'Well your search has not been in vain, for here it is.'
Golodir told you that Laerdan's breastplate might be found in Dolendath, the place where his army first took refuge after passing Rammas Deluon.
'Unfortunately, your search has also led to your doom!'
Search through Dolendath for some sign of Laerdan's breastplate.
A strange voice beckoned you forwards. Discover its source.
Your search for the source of the strange laughter led you to a gaunt-man. This vile creature must be defeated.
Search for the source of the strange laughter
